HEADWORD: Engager
<hw>En*ga"ger</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who enters into
an engagement or agreement; a surety.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Several sufficient citizens were <qex>engagers</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Wood.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Engaging</ent>⟦br⟧
